the Fine version of this file.


285
00:14:35,475 --> 00:14:39,479 line:-2
If I run the app, the new denser
texture will be used.


286
00:14:39,479 --> 00:14:41,748 line:-1
Let's take a look.


287
00:14:41,748 --> 00:14:49,256 line:-1
